animal.Joke: They say curiosity killed the cat. This is false. Chuck Norris killed the cat. Every single one of them.
Chuck Norris does not own a house. He walks into random houses and people move.
Chuck Norris once rode a nine foot grizzly bear through an automatic car wash, instead of taking a shower.

dev.Joke: Chuck Norris doesn't need garbage collection because he doesn't call .Dispose(), he calls .DropKick().
Chuck Norris doesn't need a debugger, he just stares down the bug until the code confesses.
